---
title: Cheesy Double Beef and Rigatoni Bake with Veggies and Tomato Sauce
description: This loaded cheesy bake is packed with rigatoni pasta, a creamy tomato sauce and tender, juicy beef. It's a quick, delicious dinner that's sure to be a weeknight winner!
